+ubuntu termimnal command:
  mkdir -p tutorials/src

  cd tutorials/

  ls

  catkin_make

  ls

  cd src/

  ls

+create package:
  cd src/
  catkin_create_pkg tutorial2(this is custom name of the package)   (then dependencies here if you have)
  ls
  cd tutorial2/

 +to remove a directory:               rm -rfv [name of the directory)
 +to edit the xml file there:          vim package.xml
 + to save and exit when in insert situation, press ESC and type       :wq       to save and exit.
